OL,3,CTfL launches consultation on pedicab
OL,4,Clicensing
OL,6,FTransport for London (TfL) has
OL,7,Flaunched a six-week consultation on
OL,8,Fproposals to introduce licensing and
OL,9,Fsafety regulations for pedicabs in
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,FThe transport body says it marks a
OL,13,F'key step' towards introducing new
OL,14,Frules that could come into force in
OL,15,Fearly 2026, aiming to address concerns
OL,16,Fover safety and high fares.
