OL,3,CTfL launches consultation on pedicab
OL,4,Clicensing
OL,6,FThe proposed measures include enhanced
OL,7,Fcriminal record and medical checks for
OL,8,Fdrivers, annual inspections of
OL,9,Fpedicabs covering brakes, tyres,
OL,10,Flighting, and electric batteries, as
OL,11,Fwell as regulated fares based on
OL,12,Fjourney time with a minimum charge.
OL,14,FDrivers would be required to display
OL,15,FID badges and licence plates, and
OL,16,Fexternally amplified audio on pedicabs
OL,17,Fwould be prohibited.
OL,19,FPedicabs would also only be allowed to
OL,20,Fpick up or drop off passengers where
OL,21,Fit is safe and permitted.
