OL,3,CTfL launches consultation on pedicab
OL,4,Clicensing
OL,6,FTfL says the proposals follow feedback
OL,7,Ffrom a previous consultation, in which
OL,8,Fmore than 7,500 responses were
OL,9,Freceived, highlighting concerns about
OL,10,Funsafe vehicles and overcharging.
OL,12,FThose who live in London, businesses,
OL,13,Fand pedicab operators are invited to
OL,14,Fprovide feedback on the new measures
OL,15,Funtil 20 October 2025.
OL,17,FThe Mayor of London, Sadiq Khan, said
OL,18,Fthe proposals are intended to make
OL,19,Fpedicabs safer while allowing the
OL,20,Findustry to continue operating
OL,21,Fsustainably.
